ProjectDescr.Title: HPRC Assembly
ProjectDescr.Description: This project contains assemblies generated for the Human Pangenome Reference Consortium (HPRC). The Human Pangenome Reference Consortium aims to create a collection of high-quality reference genomes that represent the genetic diversity of the human population.
